I purchased this bundle today and while I was reading the contents of the bundle it says it comes with 5 icons and a summoners ward skin in addition to the skin and champion, but in fact it came with 10 icons (one for each element). The Bundle splash art shows all 10 icons but the description says only 5.

It&#039;s not that major, but it was a pleasant surprise for me.

